ðŸ“Œ Project Overview

This project was created as a requirement for the Department of Information Technology (DIT). The main goal of this project is to practice using Docker and understand how containerization works while running a simple web application.

The project contains a basic web page built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, and it is deployed using Docker to make the application easy to run on any system.

ðŸŽ¯ Project Objectives

Learn the basics of Docker.

Understand how Docker containers work.

Practice creating and using a Dockerfile.

Run a simple web application inside a container.

